  "instructions": [
    "Roast the peanuts in a Tandoor at 450°F (230°C) for about 5-7 minutes, or until golden brown.",
    "In a blender or food processor, combine roasted peanuts, raw ginger, coconut water, ACV, and honey or agave nectar. Blend until smooth, adding cashews and sunflower seeds if using.",
